      <title>These are printed on little aluminum sign type things. Some of my art not too sh...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DU62gNRDGRd/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/639488016_18347554468239991_4185291942251564507_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpegr_e35_p1080x1080_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=102&amp;ig_cache_key=MzgzNTYxNjkwMzU5MTM5MTE3OQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTkyMC5oZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=0oU48LCHcMwQ7kNvwF0q8sW&amp;_nc_oc=AdowFu3OC9za6IOWx3pK4eugpIjDNsKOds9tPaPVQhnHUeMDqJ4BbjlhrJxinpvpsUM&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=-1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=Nj3SumAiEpy4cCkrpqjwVw&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afwg3bb1zqcr1q6HNTvy3iOqQru2Gk9IVBAi7qehwmXNYg&amp;oe=69C8E5C5" alt="Instagram billede fra @gr33d" /></p><p><strong>@gr33d</strong></p><p>These are printed on little aluminum sign type things. Some of my art not too shabby, but could be a lot better, but it’s nice to see I did kind of like a buck shot series of test prints of various mediums to see which of the vendors were quality. Sadly, with the sort of middling passability of these things came a shit lot of other horrible quality, T-shirts, etc. waste of fucking money, but I’ll keep doing it🤓</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/639488016_18347554468239991_4185291942251564507_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpegr_e35_p1080x1080_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=102&amp;ig_cache_key=MzgzNTYxNjkwMzU5MTM5MTE3OQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTkyMC5oZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=0oU48LCHcMwQ7kNvwF0q8sW&amp;_nc_oc=AdowFu3OC9za6IOWx3pK4eugpIjDNsKOds9tPaPVQhnHUeMDqJ4BbjlhrJxinpvpsUM&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=-1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=Nj3SumAiEpy4cCkrpqjwVw&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afwg3bb1zqcr1q6HNTvy3iOqQru2Gk9IVBAi7qehwmXNYg&amp;oe=69C8E5C5" alt="Instagram billede fra @gr33d" /></p><p><strong>@gr33d</strong></p><p>These are printed on little aluminum sign type things. Some of my art not too shabby, but could be a lot better, but it’s nice to see I did kind of like a buck shot series of test prints of various mediums to see which of the vendors were quality. Sadly, with the sort of middling passability of these things came a shit lot of other horrible quality, T-shirts, etc. waste of fucking money, but I’ll keep doing it🤓</p>]]></content:encoded>
